args = [Integer, List(Integer), Set(Bool), Bool, Bool]
file = StringIO()
errors = ErrorsOutput(file)
errors.max_width = 25
errors.write_supplied_arguments(args)
expected = """Supplied arguments:
    int, list of int, 
    set of bool, bool, 
    bool

"""
actual = file.getvalue()
assert expected == actual
